Package com.xrtb.nativeads.creative

This package contains all the the little pieces of a native ad bid request.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Data
    A class that represents the fields found in a bid request for a Data asset of a native ad.
    Img
    A class that encapsulates an IMG asset in a bid request for a native ad.
    Link
    A class that defines the Link asset of a native ad bid request.
    NativeCreative
    The native part of a creative.
    NativeVideo
    A class that comnprises the video part of a native ad specified in the bid request
    Title
    A class that encapsulates bid request Title asset
